data.description: BEAUTIFUL WELL-MAINTAINED HOME with a PRIMARY & GUEST SUITE in a GREAT LOCATION! 1909 Magnolia St. was built in 2005 and spans an impressive 2,393 sq ft with 4 total bedrooms (primary suite, guest suite, and 2 guest rooms), 3 baths, office/ bonus room, laundry room, and a 2-car garage.  The well-appointed kitchen offers ample storage space, granite countertops, breakfast bar, and stainless-steel appliances.  The master suite is split from all the bedrooms and features a large space, walk in closet, and a spacious shower.  Additional features include a sprinkler system, security system, privacy fence, and a large high ceiling covered patio that offers plenty of shade to stay cool and enjoy family time outside. The house is conveniently located within minutes from HEB, WALMART, Dollar General, parks, retail stores, restaurants, and schools.  Call now and SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!
